libcassandra
------------------------------------------
A C++ wrapper library for the interface to cassandra generated by thrift. This
library is based on the Java client hector.

The master branch will follow along with Cassandra trunk. Branches
corresponding to stable releases of Cassandra will be available. Downloads of
these branches are also provided.

The current master and 0.7.0 branches will work with Apache Cassandra 0.7.x.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.0.2-1
  libcassandra-devel-0.1+git20110228-1bl2
  libcassandra2-0.1+git20110228-1bl2
  libgcc1-4.9.2-3
  libgenthrift-devel-0.1+git20110228-1bl2
  libgenthrift0-0.1+git20110228-1bl2
  libstdc++6-4.9.2-3
  libthrift-devel-0.9.2-1bl1
  libthrift0.9.2-0.9.2-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-1
  cygport-0.18.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  gcc-g++-4.9.2-3
  libtool-2.4.6-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/posulliv/libcassandra

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/posulliv/libcassandra.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcassandra-0.1+git20110228-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcassandra-0.1+git20110228-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcassandra-0.1+git20110228-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcassandra-0.1+git20110228-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcassandra2-0.1+git20110228-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcassandra-devel-0.1+git20110228-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgenthrift0-0.1+git20110228-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgenthrift-devel-0.1+git20110228-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcassandra)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcassandra.README
